snippet.textDisplay:
I cried wattching this. But, I didn't really care to listen to Billie's Music. I alway's thought there was this image on her. But, that is for her to say. She is, who she is. Not, what the fan's make her out to be. Once Again I understand that if you are in the industry. It's not easy to have people putting an Agenda on you. And, other's critisizing her for how famous she is at a young age. Saying that she isn't the most depressed person in the world. But, she is depressed. And, she is a person. It has broken my heart trying to find out more about her. Her past isn't the best. But, once again that is for her to say. Your past isn't what make you who you are. Yes, they are memorie's. And, technically they do. But, don't. Any single organism is very complicated. More than we know.
For how she got here. She had so much support. And, parent's with money. The industry is the way it is. But, we can't blame her for that. Now I am a Billie Eyelash Fan lol I couldn't resist. But, seriously tho. I will dedicate myself to listen to most of her music. I've heard allot already. But, never tried to check out her album. I'm mostly happy that Phineas got an award tho. I feel her brother didn't get the credit he deserved. It's cool to see siblings's rising to the top.
